name: ipygraphql
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ipygraphql" %}
{% set version = "0.0.3" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 39f92d5c7e76412b2a00ca72e1f973a3f89b14687685dabe5891fe5e404b3b8c

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - ipywidgets >=7.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - ipygraphql

about:
  home: http://github.com/mariobuikhuizen/ipygraphql
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Graphql widgets for Jupyter'

  description: |
    Graphql widgets for Jupyter

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mariobuikhuizen
